        "id": "DS0017",
        "source": "Command",
        "component": "Command Execution",
        "description": "Monitor executed commands and arguments that may exfiltrate data to a webhook as a malicious command and control channel. Additionally, monitor commands that may create new webhook configurations in SaaS services - for example, gh webhook forward in Github or mgc subscriptions create in Office 365."
      },
